description: A quick reference for Microsoft Office 2024 Pro Plus: what’s included, key requirements, installation/deployment pointers, and common troubleshooting notes. Intended for admins and power users who want a single place to track licensing/activation considerations, supported platforms, and practical setup steps (e.g., Microsoft 365 Apps/Office Deployment Tool configs, update channels, and silent install options).  Use this gist as a living checklist: add your organization’s preferred configuration XML, standard app selection (Word/Excel/PowerPoint/Outlook/Access/Publisher, etc.), baseline policies, and any post-install scripts or remediation steps you repeatedly use.  Note: Keep licensing keys, activation scripts, and any bypass/crack instructions out of this gist.
